name: Santiago of the Seas
overview: Join Santiago, an 8-year-old pirate, and his crew as they embarks on rescues, uncover hidden treasures and keeps the Caribbean high seas safe. The show is infused with Spanish language and Latino-Caribbean culture and curriculum.

episodes.name: The Legend of Capitán Calavera
episodes.overview: Santiago and his friends become the new pirate protectors of Isla Encanto after discovering the lost treasure of the legendary Capitán Calavera.

episodes.name: The Magic Spyglass
episodes.overview: Santi and crew are after the legendary Magic Spyglass, but things get tricky when Enrique Real de Palacios III joins the chase.

episodes.name: The Stone of Life
episodes.overview: Santi and crew follow a map to a special treasure, but Bonnie and Sir Butterscotch are hot on their trail.

episodes.name: To the Lighthouse
episodes.overview: When a storm blows out the lighthouse light, Santi and crew hurry to guide Mami and Abuelo back from sea.

episodes.name: The Golden Giant
episodes.overview: When Enrique awakens a giant, Santi and crew must find a way to save the day.

episodes.name: Princess and the Pirate Puppy
episodes.overview: Santi and crew will have to team up with a pirate puppy to stop Bonnie Bones and save an old friend.

episodes.name: Caracol Cove
episodes.overview: Enrique’s new gold-digging machine threatens Lorelai’s home.

episodes.name: The Night of the Turtles
episodes.overview: When Bonnie kidnaps newly-hatched turtles before they can swim to momma out at sea, Santi and crew are on the move.

episodes.name: Santiago's Regatta
episodes.overview: Santi and crew struggle to win the Isla Encanto Regatta when Enrique starts to cheat.

episodes.name: A Pirate Christmas
episodes.overview: Santiago and crew have to help Santa save Christmas!

episodes.name: Under The Pirate Moon
episodes.overview: It's a nighttime chase above and below the sea when Escarlata turns the moon into a fish.

episodes.name: The Curse Of The Gold Falcon
episodes.overview: Santiago and crew set sail to return the Golden Falcon idol back to its rightful place.

episodes.name: The Island Of Lost Things
episodes.overview: When Santiago's magic sword is transported to the Island of Lost Things, the good pirates have to track it down by getting themselves lost!

episodes.name: Tomás' Birthday Surprise
episodes.overview: Santiago, Lorelai and Abuelo traverse treacherous waters to bring Tomás a special birthday surprise.

episodes.name: Family Treasure Hunt
episodes.overview: It's a good ol' fashioned family competition as everyone pairs up to find the fabled treasure of La Caverna Secreta.

episodes.name: Triton’s Trumpet
episodes.overview: Santiago and crew must retrieve a powerful undersea artifact after it is stolen by Enrique.

episodes.name: The Curse Of The Pirate Baby
episodes.overview: Bonnie Bones transforms into a baby, and it's up to the good pirates to change her back.

episodes.name: Santiago And Bonnie To The Rescue
episodes.overview: After getting stranded at the bottom of a crevice, Bonnie and Santiago must team up to save the day.

episodes.name: The Compass Caper
episodes.overview: Santiago is on a mad dash to get his compass back after it's nabbed by Bonnie Bones and Sir Butterscotch.

episodes.name: Deep Freeze
episodes.overview: The biggest party of the year could be cancelled after Escarlata la Pirata freezes the high seas!

episodes.name: The Trials of the Pirate Protector
The Ocelot's Tale
episodes.overview: A fun sleepover in Larimar's Museum turns into an adventure when one of the pieces of art comes to life.

episodes.name: The Lost Girl in a Canoe
The Legend of El Ratoncio Pérez
The Lost Treasure of Merlandia
episodes.overview: Anani learns of the existence of a treasure chest full of magic pearls like the one on Lorelai's bracelet. She enlists the help of the Pirate Protectors to find them.

episodes.name: Mother's Day on the High Seas
